 163:src/main.cpp  **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 3: rich power-chord bass with mixed waveforms + huge filter sweep ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 164:src/main.cpp  **** //   Mixed shapes for body: saw root (harmonic-rich), square fifth (hollow), a
