1069:src/main.cpp  ****             // 6 octaves of sweep = factor of 64x, so fully open = 32x pitch
1070:src/main.cpp  ****             // This gives the classic Moog "closed ŌåÆ wah ŌåÆ bright" feel.
1071:src/main.cpp  ****             // Power-3 on pressure so the bottom half stays dark and controlled.
